Do not book Halong Bay cruises in advance
Aug 2015 â€¢ Family
There is no need to book in advance or online. You will pay way over the odds like we did compared to when you are in Hanoi. Almost 60% more. There are literally hundreds of cruises and boats! Lots of tour agents especially if you are in the old quarter. Just book the day before.
Three nights in Hanoi is enough for me and you can have the shuttle from Halong Bay send you to the train station if you are going to SAPA by overnight train and save one night's hotel stay.
